Detailed Description

Class for holding information about user's Wayfinder subscription.

When packed into or from a packet UserWayfinderSubscription looks like this. The first TYPE and Total size in bytes and the last TYPE is read by someone else when read from a packet. {tabular}{lll} Pos & Size & Destription \ pos & 4 bytes & TYPE_WAYFINDER_SUBSCRIPTION \ +4 & 2 bytes & Total size in bytes \ +6 & 4 bytes & TYPE_WAYFINDER_SUBSCRIPTION \ +10 & 2 bytes & Total size in bytes \ +12 & 4 bytes & UserWayfinderSubscription ID \ +16 & 1 bytes & Wayfinder subscription type \ {tabular}
